static_fields.name: Divido Rubber - Ice Blue
static_fields.description: Divido's unique design is inspired by the Japanese 3-dimentional puzzle. The dial seems to be floating inside the case, suspended below the box-type sapphire crystal. Handmade in Japan and finished with the rare sallaz polishing technique.
